## Summary
This Japanese documentation page explains how to track revenue events in Amplitude, covering revenue properties ($revenue, $price, $quantity, $productId, $revenueType), in-app purchase verification using iTunes Connect and Google Play keys, and the three types of revenue events generated by SDK logRevenue calls (verified, unverified, and base revenue events).

